ive impact for our community and the planet. HRAFF definitely inspires us to do more in the area of human rights by pushing the scale of the festival every time a bit further.\r\n\r\n<em><strong><a href=\"http://www.bankaust.com.au/hraff\">Find out more about Bank Australia here.</a></strong></em>\r\n\r\n<em><strong><a href=\"http://2018.hraff.org.au/events/the-opposition-panel/\">Donâ€™t miss The Opposition Encore Screening presented by Bank Australia.</a></strong></em>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bankaust/\"><em><strong>Watch Bank Australiaâ€™s Facebook Live with The Opposition Director, Hollie Fifer on Saturday 6 May 11</strong></em><strong><em>.30am.</em></strong></a>',	'PODCAST: BANK AUSTRALIA IN CONVERSATION WITH HRAFF CHAIR AND CO-FOUNDER EVELYN TADROS',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'podcast-bank-australia-in-conversation-with-hraff-chair-and-co-founder-evelyn-tadros',	'',	'',	'2018-11-04 13:16:05',	'2018-11-04 13:16:05',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:3157/watermelon/?p=119',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
